Please listen. "Homura".

475
00:39:08,056 --> 00:39:13,556
さよなら ありがとう 声の限り
Goodbye, thank you, with all my voice

476
00:39:14,356 --> 00:39:20,556
悲しみよりもっと大事なこと
Something more important than sadness

477
00:39:21,056 --> 00:39:31,556
去りゆく背中に伝えたくて ぬくもりと痛みに間に合うように
I wanted to tell your retreating back, to make it in time with the warmth and the pain

478
00:39:32,256 --> 00:39:45,356
このまま続くと思っていた 僕らの明日を描いていた
I thought it would continue like this, I was drawing our tomorrow

479
00:39:46,056 --> 00:39:57,556
呼び合っていた光がまだ 胸の奥に熱いのに
The light that called out to each other is still hot deep in my chest

480
00:39:58,256 --> 00:40:00,056
僕たちは燃え盛る旅の途中で出会い
We met in the middle of a blazing journey

481
00:40:00,664 --> 00:40:04,564
僕たちは燃え盛る旅の途中で出会い
We met in the midst of a blazing journey

482
00:40:04,564 --> 00:40:11,064
手を取りそして離した 未来のために
We took each other's hands and then let go, for the sake of the future

483
00:40:11,564 --> 00:40:18,064
夢が一つ叶うたび 僕は君を想うだろう
Every time a dream comes true, I will probably think of you

484
00:40:18,064 --> 00:40:27,564
強くなりたいと願い 泣いた 決意を餞に
Wishing to become stronger, I cried; with determination as a parting gift

485
00:40:43,064 --> 00:40:54,564
懐かしい思いに囚われたり 残酷な世界に泣き叫んで
Being trapped in nostalgic memories, crying out to the cruel world

486
00:40:55,064 --> 00:41:06,564
大人になるほど増えて行く もう何一つだって失いたくない
Increasing as we grow up, I don't want to lose even one more thing

487
00:41:06,564 --> 00:41:20,064
悲しみに飲まれ落ちてしまえば 痛みを感なくなれるけれど
If I'm swallowed by sadness and fall, I'll stop feeling the pain, but...

488
00:41:20,564 --> 00:41:34,064
君の言葉 君の願い 僕は守りぬくと誓ったんだ
Your words, your wish; I swore to protect them to the end

489
00:41:46,064 --> 00:41:52,064
音を立てて崩れ落ちて行く
It's crumbling down with a sound

490
00:41:52,564 --> 00:42:02,564
一つだけの かけがえのない世界
The one and only, irreplaceable world

491
00:42:14,064 --> 00:42:20,064
手を伸ばし抱き止めた 激しい光の束
Reaching out and catching a fierce bundle of light

492
00:42:20,564 --> 00:42:27,064
輝いて消えてった 未来のために
It shone and then disappeared, for the sake of the future

493
00:42:27,064 --> 00:42:34,064
託された幸せと 約束を超えて行く
Going beyond the happiness and promises entrusted to me

494
00:42:34,064 --> 00:42:46,064
振り返らずに進むから 前だけ向いて叫ぶから
Because I'll move forward without looking back, because I'll look only ahead and shout

495
00:42:46,564 --> 00:42:57,064
心に炎を灯して 遠い未来まで……
Lighting a fire in my heart, until the far-off future...

496
00:43:26,564 --> 00:43:31,064
はい！ということでついにこんなね、
Yes! So, the dream of singing 'Homura'

497
00:43:31,064 --> 00:43:35,064
大舞台で炎を歌う夢が叶いました。ありがとうございます。
on such a big stage has finally come true. Thank you very much.

498
00:43:35,564 --> 00:43:39,564
いや、炎はいいよね。僕の胸もいつも燃えていますよ。
Man, 'Homura' is great, isn't it? My heart is always burning too.

