Ah, but you know, for those of you who are quick on the uptake,

501
00:43:47,064 --> 00:43:50,064
いつも僕が配信で終わる時に炎を歌ってるから、
since I always sing 'Homura' when I finish a stream,

502
00:43:50,064 --> 00:43:53,064
あ、これで終わりなんだなって思いました？
did you think 'Ah, this is the end'?

