00:50:36,080 --> 00:50:39,580
心を無にして飲みこみます
I'll empty my mind and swallow it down.

565
00:50:39,680 --> 00:50:42,580
ああ 混沌 情報過多のレストランで
Ah, chaos. In a restaurant of information overload,

